description: Input the Restore Testing Plan name and Restore Testing Selection name. All testing selections associated with a restore testing plan must be deleted before the restore testing plan can be deleted.

parameters.name: RestoreTestingPlanName
parameters.description: Required unique name of the restore testing plan that contains the restore testing selection you wish to delete.

parameters.name: RestoreTestingSelectionName
parameters.description: Required unique name of the restore testing selection you wish to delete.
